Class YAHOO.widget.Paginator.ui.LastPageLink

ui Component to generate the link to jump to the last page.

Constructor

YAHOO.widget.Paginator.ui.LastPageLink ( p )
Parameters:
p <Pagintor> Paginator instance to attach to

Properties

current - private HTMLElement

Currently placed HTMLElement node

link - private HTMLElement

Link HTMLElement node

na - private HTMLElement

Empty place holder node for when the last page link is inappropriate to display in any form (unlimited paging).

span - private HTMLElement

Span node (inactive link)

Methods

destroy

private void destroy ( )
Removes the link/span node and clears event listeners

HTMLElement render ( id_base )

void update ( e )

Configuration Attributes

lastPageLinkClass - object

CSS class assigned to the link/span
Default Value: 'yui-pg-last'

lastPageLinkLabel - object

Used as innerHTML for the last page link/span.
Default Value: 'last >>'
